{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"Orange Compact","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI."}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)"],"generated":true}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"inheritsFrom","title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Usages","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Usages"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some products may have heavy and very rich user interfaces with a lot of components and elements to displays and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with which users can interact. Thus for such products there are specific constraints of spaces and sizes, even if","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these products must be Orange flavored.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"That is the reason why this team is created: a kind of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"text":" but wih adjustments on some tokens like spacings and sizings.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the theme:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"]},{"text":"Integration","type":"heading","anchor":"Integration","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" and get it through environment variable."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeCompactTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"]},{"text":"Theme tuning","type":"heading","anchor":"Theme-tuning","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Tuning"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To apply the tuning:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"]},{"text":"Typography","type":"heading","anchor":"Typography","level":2},{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"heading","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeCompactTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\")"]},{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"heading","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"register them and define the font family name to use."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeCompactTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"]},{"text":"Tokens versions","type":"heading","anchor":"Tokens-versions","level":2},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Core OUDS version: 1.9.0","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Core Orange version: 1.2.0","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Brand Orange Compact version: 2.3.0","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange Compact"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeCompactTheme","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:23OUDSThemesOrangeCompact0bC5ThemeC","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeCompactTheme"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme"},"sections":[],"references":{"ic_theme_orangecompact.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/ic_theme_orangecompact.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orangecompact.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/SQ":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/SQ","title":"Swift.Equatable"},"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"type":"link","title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact":{"title":"Theme Orange Compact","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orangecompact.png"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange Compact theme is dedicated to applications with strong dimensions constraints."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/OrangeCompactTheme/init(fontFamily:tuning:)":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme\/init(fontfamily:tuning:)","title":"init(fontFamily:tuning:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"fontFamily","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FontFamilySemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic010FontFamilyB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tuning","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tuning","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract6Tuninga","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Constructor of the OrangeCompact theme with its own providers of tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It uses also the providers of charts colors from Orange theme (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeColorChartSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.Sendable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s8SendableP"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/OrangeCompactTheme":{"title":"OrangeCompactTheme","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/OrangeCompactTheme","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeCompactTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangecompact\/orangecompacttheme","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"Orange Compact","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to implement all tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","isActive":true},{"text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"object oriented paradigm","type":"text"}]},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme contract","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is not a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}]},{"text":" class, its type cannot be seen as ","type":"text"},{"code":"Sendable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked.","type":"text"}],"title":"OUDSTheme","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeCompact/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeCompact\/s16SendableMetatypeP"}}}